Package: scSLIDE
Type: Package
Title: Single Cell Sketching and Landmark Integrated Dimensional Embedding
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Longda", family = "Jiang", email = "ljiang@nygenome.org", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4964-6497"))
    )
Description: scSLIDE extends Seurat with advanced functionality for single-cell RNA sequencing analysis, 
    including partial least squares (PLS) dimensionality reduction, enhanced sketching methods, 
    trajectory analysis, and sample-level aggregation methods for large-scale single-cell datasets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/satijalab/scSLIDE
BugReports: https://github.com/satijalab/scSLIDE/issues
